{"tid":1269828,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"敵人係禽獸，我方係善心人，當善心人死去，禽獸只識得笑，因爲禽獸係冇「同情」基因","createTime":"2019-06-30T16:31:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T16:45:17.000Z","uid":131691,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fb66a5d7b1f923a53a435c17dc1dbfcf3fdcf7f8","tid":1269828,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T16:31:42.000Z","msg":"如果你覺得無助<br />\n請記住，香港有幾百萬人好愛你，好想幫你，好想你嘅將來變得更好<br />\n同時，有一班衣冠禽獸好想你死<br />\n<br />\n請唔好畀禽獸得逞<br />\n牢記盧梁手足嘅遺願<br />\n為已經過生嘅同路人，活得更精彩<br />\n我哋一定要勝利<br />\n我哋一定要拎返屬於我哋嘅未來<br />\n我哋一定要搶返屬於我哋嘅香港<br />\n<br />\n唔止要繼續撐<br />\n唔止要繼續走落去，活下去<br />\n仲要活得精精彩彩<br />\n因爲呢個係每一個香港人嘅職責<br />\n<br />\n因爲烈士已經失去將來<br />\n我哋可以做到最小嘅補償<br />\n就係為佢哋活出一個精彩嘅未來<br />\n好讓在天之靈<br />\n能夠微笑"},{"pid":"20a0acae99083381d52325322ba1bd011911c5cd","tid":1269828,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T16:39:43.000Z","msg":"<strong>防止自殺服務熱線</strong><br />\n如你需要援助或協助有需要人士時，請致電以下求助熱線。同時，也請鼓勵你認為有需要協助的人士致電熱線取得協助。<br />\n<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會 <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.help4suicide.com.hk&d=O1gn%2BLisHAK1lZrgQK9vXHdC2y4sA4GELDQI6FTBpyI%3D&h=5033d9d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.help4suicide.com.hk</a><br />\n<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會 <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.sbhk.org.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.sbhk.org.hk&d=O1gn%2BLisHAK1lZrgQK9vXHdC2y4sA4GELDQI6FTBpyI%3D&h=22b201e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.sbhk.org.hk</a> <br />\n電話：2389 2222<br />\n<br />\n撒瑪利亞會 <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.samaritans.org.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.samaritans.org.hk&d=O1gn%2BLisHAK1lZrgQK9vXHdC2y4sA4GELDQI6FTBpyI%3D&h=b0bd5d1f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.samaritans.org.hk</a> <br />\n電話：2896 0000"},{"pid":"50ec839c6bbb0641484da5fe37f53eeadf856b9f","tid":1269828,"uid":53498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy